  "keyFeatures": [
    "Bidirectional coach-athlete real-time platform",
    "Interactive workout mode with live timer, rest countdown, and 1RM tracking",
    "Advanced Routine Builder with day-by-day programming, RPE/RIR intensity, and templates",
    "Centralized weekly check-in and reviews with photo upload and coach feedback",
    "Skinfold (plicometría) body composition analysis using Jackson-Pollock 3/4/7-fold, Durnin-Womersley, and Yuhasz protocols",
    "Interactive progress charts: body weight, total volume, body measurements, compliance rate",
    "Real-time chat with read receipts, typing indicators, and online presence",
    "Agenda/calendar for scheduling sessions, calls, and video calls with proximity alerts",
    "Billing module for tracking subscription payments and plan status",
    "Multi-theme UI: Emerald Athletic, Iron Matte, Cyberpunk Neon, Cosmic Slate",
    "Offline-first architecture with Firebase Firestore sync and local-storage reconciliation",
    "Role-based access: Coach, Athlete (Client), and Admin panels"
  ],
